{"tid":1391404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"思考警隊高層情況 與 警民衝突 的關係","createTime":"2019-07-31T12:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T12:07:55.000Z","uid":263795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44c0065e1bb96e4b0b53be50af3cb12e4d0a7039","tid":1391404,"uid":263795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:06:23.000Z","msg":"究竟是 權力越大的人腐敗得越快 還是 腐敗得越快的人則權力越大 呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就今日警察9203的例子來說 良心警/頭腦清醒警/冷靜警是存在的 但是一般都是職位較低 並非白杉<br />\n<br />\n最近Facebook上#警員親屬連線 既group d post比我好不一樣的感覺 我覺得警民關係根本無需要到這樣覆水難收既地步 只是主因為「高層」腐敗而指揮不當，甚至繼續洗下屬腦而與民為敵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111192916880799/posts/112899590043465?s=1161976403&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111192916880799%2Fposts%2F112899590043465%3Fs%3D1161976403%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=bb964c46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111192916880799/posts/112899590043465?s=1161976403&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 當然首當其衝的，除了林鄭政府，還有警察高層的腐敗：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stimme-de.de/2019/07/30/1248/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%ad%a6%e9%9a%8a%e5%85%a7%e9%83%a8%e4%ba%ba%e7%88%86%e6%96%99%ef%bc%9a%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e8%ad%a6%e9%bb%91%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c%ef%bc%8c%e8%ad%a6%e9%9a%8a%e4%ba%8c%e5%93%a5%e7%96%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstimme-de.de%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2F1248%2F%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e9%259a%258a%25e5%2585%25a7%25e9%2583%25a8%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e7%2588%2586%25e6%2596%2599%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e9%25bb%2591%25e5%2590%2588%25e4%25bd%259c%25ef%25bc%258c%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e9%259a%258a%25e4%25ba%258c%25e5%2593%25a5%25e7%2596%2591%2F&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=0428a35c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stimme-de.de/2019/07/30/1248/%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e8%ad%a6%e9%9a%8a%e5%85%a7%e9%83%a8%e4%ba%ba%e7%88%86%e6%96%99%ef%bc%9a%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e8%ad%a6%e9%bb%91%e5%90%88%e4%bd%9c%ef%bc%8c%e8%ad%a6%e9%9a%8a%e4%ba%8c%e5%93%a5%e7%96%91/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以到最後... 我們都是被社會上掌握權力但腐敗的敗類所褻玩、玩弄、剝削、榨取、打擊、緝捕，甚至洗腦而為牠們服務。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAgain，究竟是 權力越大的人腐敗得越快 還是 腐敗得越快的人則權力越大 呢？"},{"pid":"7b792cef65cbab554ba115f360612788f99ae84b","tid":1391404,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:07:30.000Z","msg":"同我入黎一人一信<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反對黑警加人工! </span></strong></span>黑警你憑咩?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388116</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n記得要加減wordings!!!幫手推"},{"pid":"59105a1597a5f52f6a583788f85dcc5b6c8736bb","tid":1391404,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"全部手足同我推！ 如何令黑警有所顧忌有所恐懼！ 如何從狗屋內部分解黑警！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1378251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1378251</a>"}]}